title: Images of January
text:
Images of January 12:40am GMT - 01:43 
Images taken by Reuters photographers around the world for the month of January 2018, including the Grammy Awards, sentencing for Larry Nassar and a rare 'super blue blood moon' eclipse. Produced by David Lucas. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
